  "reference_number": "RUS0236",
  "remarks": "\nSince the annexation of Crimea, IS Bank, a Russian Bank, has operated across Crimea, after Ukrainian banks were stopped from operating there. Its business development is directly tied to the annexation of Crimea. In addition, it has been providing financial services, thereby facilitating the integration of Crimea into the Russian Federation through the financial system.\n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
